data.description: Charming with quality don’t begin to express the amenities listed in this one-of-a-kind, full brick home located in walking distance of downtown Meridian. Relish the idea of being able to walk to town for dinner, drinks, shopping and so much more! The entry displays the rare, coffered crown molding, original hard wood flooring, brick fireplace and large bay windows. Two spacious bedrooms on the main floor with a fully tiled bathroom. Kitchen complete with new faucet, granite counter tops, tile flooring and separate pantry. Downstairs boasts high end laminate flooring throughout done in 2023. Third bedroom had added egress window with spacious closet space. The laundry room includes a new water softener 2023, new cabinet, sink, faucet and quartz countertop. Large family room stores the second built in rock fireplace with ample windows. New plumbing in downstairs full bathroom. Step outside to enjoy the full sprinklers front/back, new roof in 2022, large 20x20 concrete patio, RV parking and alley way access!
